Abstract = {Advancements in AI, computer-aided technologies, additive manufacturing,
   and robotics are transforming the field of electromagnetics, enabling
   faster, more efficient, and cost-effective designs. This work introduces
   a computer vision based approach using open-source software to design
   antennas, offering an alternative to traditional manual methods. The
   method allows even simple hand-drawn sketches to be converted into CAD
