Month = {APR-JUN},
Abstract = {Generative AI refers to algorithms and techniques designed to generate
   text, images, videos, or other data, typically in response to prompts.
   These algorithms leverage large generative models that learn the
   patterns and structures of the media data (text, images, or videos)
   provided during training and then generate new media data that have
   analogous characteristics. Much of the recent research has gone into
   applying generative AI for text and 2-D image data. However, generative
   AI for 3-D models, especially 3-D point cloud data (PCD), has compelling
   applications in virtual reality content generation, gaming, and product
   design and manufacturing, but it introduces a multitude of research
   challenges.},
